title: [A Dark Forest Path]
description: Dense foliage moves into the small path as it disappears into the trees to the south.  With little light and plenty of places to hide, you suspect this could be an excellent spot for an ambush.

Dense foliage moves into the small path as it disappears into the trees to the south.  Shadows crisscross the ground making you feel uneasy.  With little light and plenty of places to hide, you suspect this could be an excellent spot for an ambush.
